sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户 / 渠道
    participant A as 交互接入层
    participant O as 编排控制层
    participant E as 事件存储

    U->>A: 启动请求 request_id=Q7
    A->>O: identity + session + capabilities
    O->>E: append event e101 checkpoint cp7
    O-->>A: e101 status.running
    A-->>U: event_id=e101 + resume_token
    O->>E: append e102 content.delta
    O-->>A: e102 content.delta
    A--xU: 网络断开
    O->>E: append e103 / e104 and checkpoint cp8
    U->>A: 重连 token + last_event_id=e101
    A->>A: 重验 identity session token expiry
    A->>E: read events after e101
    E-->>A: e102 e103 e104 + checkpoint cp8
    loop 按 event_id 有序补发
        A->>A: 跳过客户端已确认或重复事件
        A-->>U: replay event + idempotent cursor
    end
    A->>O: resume from cp8 + acknowledged=e104
    O-->>A: e105 current status / result
    A-->>U: e105 + new resume_token
    alt token 过期 身份变化或事件已清理
        A-->>U: resume_unavailable + restart / handoff
    end
